text: The steamed dumplings are quite good, with solid and clean meat, plenty of filling inside, and a beautifully crafted outer skin. The wonton soup is excellent, with small wontons that taste quite nice.
I had the Set A wanton soup with dry noodles... very savory and nice! Aunty was very friendly also.
Nice stall. Friendly staff. The onion noodles, wanton and steamed dumpling are nice. Reasonable pricing for coffeeshop.

the fried rice, fried noodles with meat are nice. the dumplings are nice. but i dont like their "meat" soup - the meat feels like mock meat. the dry noodles have a slight kind of "smell" that i dont like. staff are very friendly. great value for money.
